### **4. 33_LiveDataChartPanel**  
**Description:**  
Plots a real-time line chart from incoming numeric data using Matplotlib.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveDataChartPanel - Real-Time Data Visualization

LiveDataChartPanel is a minimal tool for monitoring and visualizing numeric data on a continuously updating chart.

## Features
- Live chart updates  
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Lightweight & portable  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/33_LiveDataChartPanel.git
cd 33_LiveDataChartPanel
python visualize.py
